item.title: CVE-2018-1247|2024-09-16T16:39:05.452Z -- dell%20emc -- rsa%20authentication%20manager%20security%20console
item.description: RSA Authentication Manager Security Console, version 8.3 and earlier, contains a XML External Entity (XXE) vulnerability. This could potentially allow admin users to cause a denial of service or extract server data via injecting a maliciously crafted DTD in an XML file submitted to the application.
